Subject: [PATCH] Fix broken repository_url in 6 METADATA.pb files
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Red Hat Display/Mono/Text: bghryct/* (deleted) → RedHatOfficial/RedHatFont
  Also adds config_yaml paths and updates file paths for new repo structure
- Manrope: sharanda/manrope (deleted) → aaronbell/manrope
  Also adds commit hash and config_yaml
- Orelega One: JapanYoshi/Orelega (deleted) → gitlab.com/haleyhalcyon/orelega
  Designer migrated from GitHub to GitLab
- Elsie: Remove invalid URL "googlefonts/elsiefont (404)"
  Sources are genuinely lost; no upstream repo exists

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
